Complex_NetAmountWithShipAndTaxes.sql:
SELECT i_item_sk ws_item_sk,
word_order_id ws_order_number,
((wlin_sales_price * wlin_quantity)-wlin_coupon_amt + (wlin_ship_cost * wlin_quantity))
* (1 + web_tax_percentage) as WS_NET_PAID_INC_SHIP_TAX
FROM
s_web_order
JOIN s_web_order_lineitem ON (word_order_id = wlin_order_id)
LEFT OUTER JOIN item ON (wlin_item_id = i_item_id AND i_rec_end_date IS NULL) 
LEFT OUTER JOIN web_site ON (word_web_site_id = web_site_id AND web_rec_end_date IS NULL) order by ws_item_sk, ws_order_number
